WEBVTT

00:00:27.462 --> 00:00:30.803
"To'rt mavsum" dan
"Bahor" konsertining kirish qismi.

00:00:30.803 --> 00:00:35.031
"To'rt fasl" ko'proq eshituvchiga o'zgacha
zavq bag'ishlagani tufayli mashhur.

00:00:35.031 --> 00:00:36.542
Ammo yanada diqqatga sazovor

00:00:36.542 --> 00:00:39.572
haqiqat shundaki,
ularning aytib beradigan hikoyalari bor.

00:00:39.572 --> 00:00:43.352
"To'rt mavsum" ning 1725 yil
Amsterdamda nashr etilgan partiturasiga

00:00:43.352 --> 00:00:44.883
she'rlar hamrohlik qilgan

00:00:44.883 --> 00:00:47.522
va ular Vivaldining ayni faslga
xos qaysi holatni

00:00:47.522 --> 00:00:50.982
tasvirlashini maqsad qilganligini
hikoya qilgan.

00:00:50.982 --> 00:00:53.963
Cholg'u musiqasi uchun o'ziga xos
mazmunli syujet yaratishda

00:00:53.963 --> 00:00:57.877
Vivaldi o'z davridan
bir necha avlod oldinda edi.

00:00:57.877 --> 00:01:01.483
Agar-da kimdir musiqani eshitish bilan
birga she'rlarni o'qiganida,